explains: adj. 未经确认的；未辨别出的，身份不明的

sentences.en: The document was excerpted from an unidentified FBI file.
sentences.cn: 此文件摘自来源不明的联邦调查局档案。

sentences.en: He was shot this morning by unidentified intruders at his house.
sentences.cn: 他今天早晨在家里遭到身份不明的闯入者枪击。

sentences.en: Catherine found a blank, unidentified envelope.
sentences.cn: 凯瑟琳找到了一封来源不明的空白信封。
